===Noun===
'''[[Amami]] [[rabbit]]'''
#''[[Pentalagus furnessia]]'', a  primitive dark-furred [[rabbit]] found on two islands ([[Amami]] and Toku-no-Shima) in southern Japan. A noctural, forest-dwelling animal with short legs, a somewhat bulky body, rather large and curved claws. Its ears are significantly smaller than those of other rabbits or hares.
